uttonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 22, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104ber1665702754637.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ber1665702754637.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ber1665702754637.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"ber1665702754637\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      /mod\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Specifies a model name for Uniface objects that are added when importing WSDL definitions for call-out.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ber1665702754637__section_w2988ab1b5b1_w2989ab1b5_w2990ab1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ber1665702754637__p_d150302e1_d150303e1_d150304e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">/mod=</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">ModelName</var>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ber1665702754637__section_w2991ab1b5b3_w2992ab1b5_w2993ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d854119e63\">\n                  \n Used With\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ber1665702754637__d6988e20\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"khj1665702753156.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/khj1665702753156.html\" title=\"Import interface definitions to integrate call-out to web services, various types of middleware, or to generate C call-in stub code for all types of components.\">/sti</a>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ber1665702754637__section_w2994ab1b5b5_w2995ab1b5_w2996ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d854119e79\">\n                  \n Parameters\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ber1665702754637__p_d150314e1_d150315e1_d150316e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">ModelName</var>—new or existing model name; maximum 32 characters, starting with alphabetic character.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ber1665702754637__section_w2997ab1b5b7_w2998ab1b5_w2999ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d854119e91\">\n                  \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ber1665702754637__p_d150320e1_d150321e1_d150322e1\">If <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/mod=</span>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">ModelName</var> is specified, it overrides the default model name, which is derived from the first element of the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Model</span> property of the entity.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ber1665702754637__p_d150326e1_d150327e1_d150328e1\">If there is no existing model with the specified name, an application model is generated and added to the Repository.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ber1665702754637__p_d150329e1_d150330e1_d150331e1\">If a model name begins with non-alphabetic characters, they are removed from the name. If the resulting name is null, the name <code class=\"ph codeph\">FILLER</code> is generated.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2526009\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2526009\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "/mod Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 22, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 /mod Specifies a model name for Uniface objects that are added when importing WSDL definitions for call-out. /mod= ModelName Used With /sti Parameters ModelName —new or existing model name; maximum 32 characters, starting with alphabetic character. Description If /mod= ModelName is specified, it overrides the default model name, which is derived from the first element of the Model property of the entity. If there is no existing model with the specified name, an application model is generated and added to the Repository. If a model name begins with non-alphabetic characters, they are removed from the name. If the resulting name is null, the name FILLER is generated. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}